    "description": "<header><div class=\"inner\"><nav><a href=\"https://stores.ebay.com/Deals-Only-Web-Store\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"logo\">Deals<span class=\"logo-bold\">Only</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"nav\"><label for=\"nav\"></label>\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"margin-killer-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"margin-killer-left\"><a href=\"https://stores.ebay.com/Deals-Only-Web-Store\" target=\"_blank\">Store</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/cnt/intermediatedFAQ?requested=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">About</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\t<main>\n\t\t<div class=\"section-row full\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-50 right section-body\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section-head full\">Product Benefits</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"section-feature\">SINGLE PIECE FORGED CONSTRUCTION: Extremely durable and able to withstand a constant pounding whether it is for rock hounding geology or home construction use, alike</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"section-feature\">ANTI-FATIGUE RUBBER GRIP: Featuring a ergonomic injection molded handle, designed to help reduce the pressure from the constant vibrations of repeated material striking while hunting for lost dinosaur bones in the field</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"section-feature\">SQUARE FACE with PICK: Use the pointed tip to break open rock and loosen sediment while utilizing the square hammer face to drive chisels; splitting rocks</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"section-feature\">SPECIFICATIONS: Overall Length: 11 inches; Overall Weight: 32oz; Head Weight: 20oz&nbsp;</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"section-feature\">Provides the perfect balance and power-to-weight ratio to increase swing speed and intensify striking power</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-50 left section-body\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"section-head full\">Item details</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-25 left section-key\">Includes:</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-75 left\"><span class=\"text-inline\">(1) Rock Pick Hammer</span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<hr class=\"new-row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-25 left section-key\">Condition:</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-75 left\">New</div>\n\t\t\t\t<hr class=\"new-row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-25 left section-key\">Brand:</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-75 left\">ASR Outdoor</div><div class=\"grid-75 left\"><br></div>\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<hr class=\"new-row\">\n\t\t<div class=\"grid-100 section-body\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"product-title\">20oz Ergonomic Rock Pick Mining Masonry Hammer by ASR Outdoor</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"text\">This ASR Outdoor Ergonomic Rock Pick Hammer is durable and ideal for a mid-range, economical geology or hobbyist tool box. The 11-inch rock pick hammer as its made to take a beating and dish out one out. The ergonomic anti-shock rubber molded handle makes it comfortable to hold and gives comfort while absorbing the vibrations from the constant striking of material. Added head control is benefited from the handle being constructed from a soft rubber grip while also providing against accidental slipping while in the field. \n\nHone in on your rock hounding and hunting capabilities with the ASR Outdoor Rock Pick Hammer. This is an absolute must have for any aspiring prospector. Other industrial uses can be used for this model as well since the dual head consisting of a hammer end and pointed pick It is perfect for breaking and chipping bricks, concrete, masonry stones and rocks in masonry construction, gold prospecting, gem collecting, general mining, university geologizing and many more industries\n\nThere are no frills or hidden agendas with this item; it is made to take a beating and dish one out.</span>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<hr class=\"new-row\">\n<div class=\"grid-100 section-body\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-head